{"type":"text","timestamp":1781144281264,"sessionID":"ses_14b8a0226ffeqM34sND4WLFHSs","part":{"id":"prt_eb478dc920014fB6Ndm3RHR3Ru","messageID":"msg_eb47837480010k4C2GAATm665l","sessionID":"ses_14b8a0226ffeqM34sND4WLFHSs","type":"text","text":"I found concrete review findings rather than a clean pass: the new `VectorStore` port does not preserve caller-supplied record identity in the better-sqlite implementation, and `clear()` deletes metadata tables despite the interface saying vector records. I’m writing the lineage state now with max-iteration stop and a `CONDITIONAL` synthesis.","time":{"start":1781144280210,"end":1781144281262},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0d7d1532794d5417016a2a1ad82ce48191b8d1beb2b81c0079","phase":"commentary"}}}}
